see them through to completion. Strong understanding of formal project management methodologies, Agile in particular. 5+ years of experience working in a similar role. ???????????? Bonus if you also have... Experience with the fundamentals of blockchain technology, developer platforms, game design, and / or token economics ???????????? Benefits We believe in treating people right to build a great team for the journey ahead. If there\u2019s something important to you that\u2019s not on this list, talk to us! :) Competitive compensation. Remote and/or flexible work arrangements. We believe in bringing on the best people to our team no matter where they are in the world. A dynamic startup environment where you will constantly be challenged and exposed to new ideas. Whatever equipment helps you get your job done. ???????????? About Forte Headquartered in San Francisco, Forte is developing blockchain technology platforms and products built for the games industry. By tackling hard technology problems behind the scenes, Forte is forging a more collaborative future between game developers, players and creators. The founding team of Forte is composed of experts in game platform development, game design and publishing from leading companies such as Kabam, GarageGames, Unity, Linden Lab, and Gen.G Esports.???????????? ", 
